name: Web Source 1" (24mm) Nylon Flat Climbing Webbing
description: Appropriate for climbing applications that don't require the strength of pre-sewn slings. Variety of colours available, lets you use a different colour to indicate different sling lengths.This product is sold by the metre.Made of nylon.24mm width.Breaking strength is approximately 20kN (2041kg).Note: tying a knot in webbing reduces strength and does not meet the CE sling standard of 22kN, which is achievable with pre-sewn slings.
